Dumping lctl log to /tmp/test_logs/1481926605/sanity.test_311.*.1481926744.log
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After investigating i think statfs doesn&apos;t update in timely manner. So first &apos;lfs df&apos; may not reflect real filesystem statistic. So we should consider doing a sync action while &apos;lfs df&apos; in first place. Will push a patch for it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
